**DECISION**

PROMULGATING THE REGULATION ON THE USE MANAGEMENT OF CONDOMINIUMS

**THE MINISTER OF CONSTRUCTION**

_Pursuant to the Governments Decree No. 15/CP of March 4, 1994 prescribing the functions, tasks, powers and organizational structure of the Ministry of Construction;  
